### Plotting Figure 1


a. Simulating coordinates of labels on the map

simulate_point_locations.R

requirements:
samples_locations.txt


b. Plotting a map with strains

map_geo.R

requirements:
samples_locations.txt
simulated_coords.txt
world_intermediate.txt


c. Plotting picture of a globe

plotGlobe.R


d. Plotting NJ phylogeny

plotTree.py

requirements:
NewickExport_fasttree.nwk
Species_distinction_PCA.txt


e. Plotting structure

plotStructure.R

requirements:
Structure_genomewide_results_K2.csv
Structure_genomewide_results_novoulmi_K2.csv
Structure_genomewide_results_novoulmi_K3.csv
Species_distinction_PCA.txt
plotTree_strain_order.txt


f. Plotting PCA

PCA_Plot.R

requirements:
Species_distinction_PCA.txt
scores_pca.txt


